test_even_range:
assert [2, 4] == [4]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 4
  Full diff:
  - [4]
  + [2, 4]
test_large_range:
assert [1, 2] == [2]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Left contains one more item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2]
  + [1, 2]
test_zero_range:
assert [0, 0] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 0]
